# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  CLIENT — any authenticated user
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Search / Autocomplete ────────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Search — with query term
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/search?q=r
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Search — partial match (returns python, pytorch, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/search?q=py
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Search — no query → top 10 most used skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Search — match on alias (e.g. "JS" maps to JavaScript)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/search?q=JS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ Search — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/search?q=java


# ─── Propose a new skill ─────────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Create — new skill, will be pending_review
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Darija marocaine",
  "category": "languages"
  
}

### ✅ Create — duplicate name → returns existing skill (no error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Darija marocaine",
  "category": "languages"
}

### ❌ Create — invalid category (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Some Skill",
  "category": "music"
}

### ❌ Create — name too short (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "A",
  "category": "tech"
}

### ❌ Create — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Skill",
  "category": "tech"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  ADMIN — role: admin required (use @adminToken)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── List all skills ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Admin — list all skills (all statuses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ Admin — filter by status: pending_review
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills?status=pending_review
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ Admin — filter by status: approved
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills?status=approved
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ Admin — filter by status: rejected
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills?status=rejected
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ Admin — with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills?status=pending_review&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ❌ Admin — regular user token (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ─── Pending review shortcut ──────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Admin — pending skills (review screen)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ❌ Admin — regular user token (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ─── Approve ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Admin — approve a skill
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ❌ Admin — approve already approved skill (400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ❌ Admin — regular user cannot approve (403)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ Admin — skill not found (404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


# ─── Reject ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Admin — reject with a reason
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "reason": "Doublon avec une compétence existante."
}

### ✅ Admin — reject without a reason (reason is optional)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{}

### ❌ Admin — reject already rejected skill (400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{}

### ❌ Admin — regular user cannot reject (403)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}


# ─── Aliases ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### ✅ Admin — set aliases on a skill (improves autocomplete)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/aliases
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "aliases": ["JS", "ECMAScript", "Vanilla JS"]
}

### ✅ Admin — clear aliases
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/{{skillId}}/aliases
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "aliases": []
}

### ❌ Admin — skill not found (404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/skills/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/aliases
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "aliases": ["test"]
}
